  "title": "Service Crew (Cafe)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong><br>\n <br>\n • Greet customers courteously and assist them with their orders, if needed.</p>\n<p>• Prepare and serve beverages consistent with company’s quality standards.<br>\n • Serve customers with their food.</p>\n<p>• Maintain beverage making appliances/equipment in a functional and clean manner to support efficient beverage making.</p>\n<p>• Perform cashier’s duties</p>\n<p>• Clean and maintain the café areas including washing of table wares etc<br>\n • Assist in the stocking and replenishment of beverage supplies.</p>\n<p>• Follow the company’s security &amp; safety procedures, hygiene &amp; service practices.</p>\n<p>• Perform any other duties as and when required by the Management.<br>\n <br>\n <strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p>\n<p>• Preferably with 1 years’ relevant experience and a valid food safety course level 1 certificate.</p>\n<p>• Minimum secondary school education</p>\n<p>• Willing to work on weekends and public holidays (for part time staff: Thursday – Sunday full shift). Shifts: 9am – 6pm and 12 – 9pm.<br>\n• Able to work independently and support other team members proactively</p>\n<p>in a fast-paced environment</p>",
